Author: many_mishaps_melly
Text: It sounds like you know what you need lovely. Try something small like and apple, or some red pepper pieces or something small but colourful.  I like to think to myself "yum, this is so fresh and good!" when I eat raw vegetables to try and get that truth to be normal.

Author: CloudySideDown
Text: It shouldn't. Try to eat something. And to not beat yourself up over it even if it's more than you planned. Having energy is worth it.
